{"tid":371710,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"90後梨大賣港式美食　靚韓妹為你整紅豆冰","createTime":"2017-08-24T00:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T10:31:08.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c90b4af133aaa9e23e14da58104ff98eab412e5c","tid":371710,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941846_589e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941846_589e.jpg&h=f88e3c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n90後阿亨喺梨大開港韓cafe，賣港式飲品同美食。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941847_f4a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941847_f4a0.jpg&h=0a34a089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚靚韓妹Hye Jin識整紅豆冰，仲用廣東話講，「好味呀！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941848_7798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941848_7798.jpg&h=652c3480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿亨空運黑白淡奶同錫蘭茶葉去首爾，沖正宗港式奶茶，一杯賣₩5000(約$35)。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941849_0ed5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941849_0ed5.jpg&h=34781d03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富有香港特色嘅蛋達、雞蛋仔、西多士等都有得賣。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941851_96a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941851_96a4.jpg&h=5c276907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開cafe加入茶餐廳概念，係因為阿亨屋企人真係開茶餐廳。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941856_eade.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941856_eade.jpg&h=db230b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然阿亨係老闆，但係好多事都要親力親為。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941852_c010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941852_c010.jpg&h=80fabfa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ncafe內有唔少港式擺設同裝飾。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941853_71a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941853_71a1.jpg&h=c431e257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿亨兩年前喺梨大語學堂讀韓文，每日返學都經過自己租嘅舖位，當時仲係吉嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502941854_6c55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502941854_6c55.jpg&h=6ed9733a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n間舖地理位置非常好，就距離地鐵站一分鐘路程。<br />\n<br />\n一杯香滑奶茶係唔少香港人早餐必備，亦係唔少遊客嚟香港必飲，咁正嘅嘢，畀一位90後港男帶到首爾，喺梨大開咗間港韓cafe Charcoal。《仙遊首爾》第四集專訪只係得25歲就榮升老闆嘅周俊亨。<br />\n<br />\n點解話係港韓cafe？因為一般韓國cafe有嘅嘢，例如Americano、Mocha、Espresso等，呢到有，一般韓國cafe無嘅，例如絲襪奶茶、紅豆冰、鴛鴦等，呢到都有，仲有得食蛋撻、雞蛋仔、西多士等，簡直係搬咗半間茶餐廳去首爾！<br />\n<br />\n阿亨話想將奶茶文化帶到韓國，所以用返最正宗嘅黑白淡奶同錫蘭茶葉，做出真正嘅香港味道。首先被影響嘅，係做兼職嘅靚靚韓妹Hye Jin，唔止學識沖奶茶，仲識整紅豆冰，佢仲用廣東話講，「好味呀！」Hye Jin每逢周末坐陣，為你落單，為你沖調各款港式飲品。<br />\n<br />\n開業頭兩個月，阿亨話多數係住喺韓國嘅香港人嚟幫襯，「之前都唔知原來咁多香港人住喺韓國。」之後啲韓國人嚟過，覺得幾得意，喺網上share，就越嚟越多韓國客人，亦都有唔少熟客係梨花女子大學嘅學生。阿亨話o依家啱啱交到租，出到糧，至於幾時可以返本都係未知數。<br />\n<br />\n阿亨唔係哈韓族，同韓國結緣係因為18歲嗰年，喺美國LA讀大學主修韓國文學，兩年前再喺梨花女子大學讀韓文，就喺返學途中，每日都經過當時仲係吉嘅兩層舖。由構思，到實踐，到真正開到舖，年紀輕輕就榮升老闆，阿亨有四大優勢，詳情請睇片！<br />\n<br />\n記者：阿仙<br />\n攝影：峰、Neo<br />\n編審：Kaman<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170824/57091613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170824%2F57091613&d=ZXwma8W0dXeta1FKeUUtbxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3b1e999c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170824%2F57091613&h=28e149af\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170824/57091613</a>"},{"pid":"2cecfbe3b0192b01a7aa8e5b161be3f9b3868eb7","tid":371710,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:29:26.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"949cda8c6fd6891b9ed3e828422410ec22fc3641","tid":371710,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:33:34.000Z","msg":"有錢有成功系列"},{"pid":"3a129b293f8b7dd02e3de082c84afe2891528010","tid":371710,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"個度好多cafe<br />\n連全韓國第一間starfuck都係個度"},{"pid":"dc49c17d43f4f6d55d7e6c691a2a579be607fa29","tid":371710,"uid":134462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:38:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7eafce756d557e75473dd708b6bdf6aabbd367e","tid":371710,"uid":7206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"係美國讀韓國文學係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5556b2e6a0d2333c139449131a9cc201e72dbf47","tid":371710,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T00:46:53.000Z","msg":"特登去LA讀韓文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e228eea9ee3e5662e9d5929f7870bb4bcfb0bed1","tid":371710,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"點解男人可以係梨花女子大學讀韓文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380df6d5f859c63880025adf425e240e18aaf92f","tid":371710,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"哦<img sr